sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI
    participant API
    participant Asset as Asset Service
    participant Agent as OpenAI Agents Runtime
    participant Queue
    participant Provider as Image Provider
    participant Store as Object Storage
    participant DB

    User->>UI: 输入 prompt + 上传素材
    UI->>API: POST message / upload complete
    API->>Asset: 解析素材
    Asset->>DB: 写入 MaterialBrief
    API->>Agent: Runner.run(session, message, asset_ids)
    Agent->>Agent: Intent -> PromptPlan -> ProviderDecision
    Agent->>API: create_image_job tool
    API->>Queue: enqueue image job
    Queue->>Provider: generate/edit image
    Provider-->>Queue: base64 / URL / bytes
    Queue->>Store: 转存输出和缩略图
    Queue->>DB: job ready + output records
    API-->>UI: SSE job.status + output
    UI-->>User: 展示画廊
